            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "The MS Vasundhara branch has been closed forever and communicated to parents on 18th March when all the schools are done with admissions. The students in MS Vasundhara have no option but to waste their whole year. MS gave RNEx as an alternative but parents are not ready cos of distance/infra/teacher etc but few are forced to do so cos of no other option left. This was well planned by MS Management. Highly unethical & immoral decision to increase the no. of students at MS RNEx while playing with the future of the students at Vasundhara Branch. They knew that parents won't send their kids to some 15 KMs each side wasting time/money and risking their safety as well on a sub-standard facilities if they would have announced this in Dec/Jan.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
