            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I will definitely recommend THE MODERN EARLY YEARS. This name itself is saying everything. My daughter has truly blossomed over the past two years academically and socially. She is always eager to go to school and has a wonderful relationship with her teachers. The principal and teachers make themselves very accessible and very supportive in every little issues. The well designed study curriculum and fun-filled activities here at Modern also help to enrich students.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
